             was indicted for <rs id="t18191027-20-off111" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18191027-20-off111" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18191027-20-off111" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18191027-20-cd112" type="crimeDate">2d of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191027-20-off111 t18191027-20-cd112"></join>, one umbrella, value 5 s.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18191027-20-victim249" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Wakeman
                  <interp inst="t18191027-20-victim249" type="surname" value="Wakeman"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18191027-20-victim249" type="given" value="James"></interp>
